In order to receive TAFDC, an applicant or client must meet all of the applicable eligibility requirements. These requirements are both nonfinancial and financial.

The nonfinancial requirements for TAFDC eligibility are:

(A) Exemptions from Time-Limited Benefits and Reduced Need and Payment Standards, 106 CMR 703.100;

(B) Time-Limited Benefits, 106 CMR 703.120;

(C) Reserved;

(D) Work Program, 106 CMR 703.150;

