Assistance in the form of vendor payments is required when the grantee does not meet the requirements of:

(A) the Employment Services Program (ESP) as provided in 106 CMR 707.000, et seq;

(B) the Child Support Enforcement Division (CSED) of the Department of Revenue as provided in 106 CMR 703.500 through 703.530;

(C) the Work Program as provided in 106 CMR 703.150;

(D) Immunizations as provided in 106 CMR 703.160;

(E) cooperation with the Department in identifying and providing information that would assist the Department in pursuing any third-party liability for medical services as provided in 106 CMR 703.540;

